[For the location of Kinmen County, an island close to mainland China, see https://tinyurl.com/yaobfcqv.

A 2nd dead pig was spotted Friday [4 Jan 2019] on a beach in Xiaoqiu islet, Kinmen County, 4 days after the finding of the 1st carcass, at another coastal location in Kinmen. The 2nd dead pig was believed to be brought by the tide, as there are no pig farms on the Kinmen-administrated islet, said Coast Guard Administration (CGA) Director-General Lee Chung-wei. Tests of this case are being applied, with results expected soon. For more details, refer to http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201901040007.aspx. - Mod.AS

